ReticleFix
=================
Bring back reticles to Call of Duty: Black Ops 2!

This application does:

1. Copy itself to Steam/steamapps/common/Call of Duty Black Ops II/ReticleFix.exe
2. Modify installscript.vdf to launch ReticleFix.exe when starting game.
3. Set "Deny Write" permission to installscript.vdf to prevent Steam is reverting to original.
4. Disable/Enable all display adapters when starting game.